MATT: The only feature
request that I've

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:03.520
made to them-- although
they responded super quick.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:06.010
They were like, yeah, it's way
harder than you think it is.

00:02:06.010 --> 00:02:08.949
It's if someone raises a pull
request against a new repo,

00:02:08.949 --> 00:02:11.370
say, you'll get a
notification saying,

00:02:11.370 --> 00:02:13.290
oh, there's a new pull
request, new thing.

00:02:13.290 --> 00:02:13.840
That's fine.

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:16.580
