knew that that's what happened.

00:02:34.290 --> 00:02:36.720
But it's not surfaced anywhere.

00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:39.820
But beyond that, this
thing is perfect for me.

00:02:39.820 --> 00:02:40.920
I love it.

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:43.200
The other tool, and the
reason they got a new update,

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:45.690
is Greenkeeper.

00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:48.360
The change that they've made
it's much more integrated with

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:50.450
get GitHub now in terms
of just being an app,

00:02:50.450 --> 00:02:51.280
and it is amazing.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:55.680
So what Greenkeeper does is it
manages all your MPM modules.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.480
So if there's a new
version, it will

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:00.855
create a new PR that
will basically say here's

00:03:00.855 --> 00:03:03.960
the version being
pumped for you.

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:04.680
Love it.

00:03:04.680 --> 00:03:06.780
