to do is you can just

00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:09.750
go through their
process, configure it,

00:03:09.750 --> 00:03:12.889
and it will basically sit there
and give you all of the repos

00:03:12.889 --> 00:03:14.180
that you want to enable it for.

00:03:14.180 --> 00:03:16.429
So you can do it for all of
them or just a select few.

00:03:16.429 --> 00:03:18.810
I just handpicked the ones I
know that I want to babysit.

